# Playlinko Web — Design System Rules

Adapted from the production game's design standards (linko-prism/SKILL.md §7).

---

## 1. Warm Amber Glass Theme — Token Reference

| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode |
|---|---|---|
| Background gradient | `#FFFBEB → #FEF3C7 → #FDE68A` | `#0F0700 → #1C0E02 → #2A1500` |
| Primary accent | `#F59E0B` (amber-500) | same — glows brighter |
| Heading text | `#78350F` (amber-900) | `#FDE68A` (amber-200) |
| Body text | `#B45309` (amber-700) | `#FCD34D` (amber-300) |
| Muted / metadata | `#D97706` (amber-600) at 50–70% | `rgba(252,211,77,0.70)` |
| Glass card bg | `rgba(255,255,255,0.58)` | `rgba(45,25,5,0.72)` |
| Glass nav bg | `rgba(255,251,235,0.82)` | `rgba(15,7,0,0.90)` |

---

## 2. Text Contrast — Hard Rules

**Every text element must meet WCAG AA (≥ 4.5:1 contrast) against its background in BOTH light and dark modes.**

### Minimum colours per surface

| Surface | Light mode min | Dark mode min |
|---|---|---|
| Glass card (`rgba(255,255,255,0.58)`) | `text-amber-700` (#B45309) | `#FCD34D` (amber-300) |
| Glass nav (`rgba(255,251,235,0.82)`) | `text-amber-700` | `#FDE68A` (amber-200) |
| Dark body background | — | `#FDE68A` (amber-200) |
| Amber CTA buttons (primary) | white (`#ffffff`) | white (`#ffffff`) |

### Approved colour pairs (tested)

| Text | Background | Contrast ratio | Use for |
|---|---|---|---|
| `#78350F` amber-900 | white card | 8.1:1 ✓ | Headings, names |
| `#92400E` amber-800 | white card | 6.3:1 ✓ | Sub-headings |
| `#B45309` amber-700 | white card | 4.7:1 ✓ | Body copy |
| `#FDE68A` amber-200 | `#2D1905` dark card | 9.1:1 ✓ | Headings in dark |
| `#FCD34D` amber-300 | `#2D1905` dark card | 7.4:1 ✓ | Body in dark |
| `rgba(252,211,77,0.70)` | `#2D1905` dark card | ~5.2:1 ✓ | Muted/metadata in dark |

